00:44:21,967 --> 00:44:23,869
or somebody can just blow it out themselves

866
00:44:23,969 --> 00:44:27,675
and just do it, or charge $100 and have it be

867
00:44:27,815 --> 00:44:29,217
like an art project kind of a thing

868
00:44:29,257 --> 00:44:31,400
where it's just a very limited audience.

869
00:44:31,820 --> 00:44:34,204
There used to be, with James Earnest,

