00:45:13,032 --> 00:45:15,573
that went very long and I had paper in front of me

881
00:45:15,773 --> 00:45:18,414
and I decided to try to design a simple game.

882
00:45:18,434 --> 00:45:20,875
And I sort of got to a point where I was obsessed with it,

883
00:45:21,015 --> 00:45:22,316
probably to an unhealthy degree,

884
00:45:22,616 --> 00:45:24,197
and I was forcing my friends to play test it

885
00:45:24,217 --> 00:45:26,357
and it was like actually straining a lot of my friendships.

886
00:45:26,918 --> 00:45:29,339
And so it was really strange.

887
00:45:29,719 --> 00:45:31,840
And then, so I kind of like let it drop.

888
00:45:32,380 --> 00:45:34,281
due to social pressure mostly, and I was like kind of,

889
00:45:34,581 --> 00:45:37,123
I kind of hit a roadblock like you were describing.

890
00:45:37,483 --> 00:45:39,825
And then now, like a couple weeks ago,

891
00:45:39,945 --> 00:45:41,266
I noticed that there was like a game

892
00:45:41,326 --> 00:45:43,007
that's coming out soon that has a lot of,

