00:46:21,926 --> 00:46:23,827
you focus on something else, and then six months later,

905
00:46:24,187 --> 00:46:25,528
something very similar comes out, and you go,

906
00:46:25,688 --> 00:46:27,649
oh, I almost had it, you know what I mean?

907
00:46:29,530 --> 00:46:31,111
Particularly that latter one, is that a thing

