00:48:03,980 --> 00:48:07,841
a good game, at least not now, maybe not ever. And the hard part as a game designer

931
00:48:07,881 --> 00:48:08,521
is figuring out

932
00:48:08,981 --> 00:48:09,701
when you're stuck.

933
00:48:10,422 --> 00:48:12,222
versus when it's a bad idea.

934
00:48:12,602 --> 00:48:14,082
Because you're gonna get to that point where

935
00:48:14,362 --> 00:48:15,143
you're stuck and you're like,

936
00:48:15,303 --> 00:48:16,263
I'll just start the next thing

937
00:48:16,283 --> 00:48:17,383
because it's shiny and it's easy

938
00:48:17,403 --> 00:48:18,623
and it doesn't have any problems yet.

939
00:48:18,983 --> 00:48:21,044
