00:48:33,628 --> 00:48:36,970
I've seen games where I had like half an idea and then two years later someone came and

948
00:48:36,990 --> 00:48:40,332
was like, yeah that was my idea but they did the work, they did the sweat to do it and

949
00:48:40,372 --> 00:48:41,192
they had it come out.

950
00:48:41,212 --> 00:48:46,696
There are a lot of games that are like a lot of other games and you know, you can still

951
00:48:46,716 --> 00:48:48,577
keep working on a game if it's similar to another game.

952
00:48:48,597 --> 00:48:49,357
Just make it your own.

953
00:48:50,038 --> 00:48:50,518
It'll be different.

954
00:48:51,775 --> 00:48:52,035
