1239
01:05:28,417 --> 01:05:30,479
mechanics to it, and then kind of a follow up?

1240
01:05:31,339 --> 01:05:33,060
Have we reached peak Cthulhu yet?

1241
01:05:33,180 --> 01:05:35,241
