1242
01:05:35,281 --> 01:05:36,722
No, no, there's no peak Cthulhu.

1243
01:05:36,802 --> 01:05:38,343
It's Cthulhu all the way down.

1244
01:05:38,423 --> 01:05:39,464
Always room for Cthulhu.

1245
01:05:39,804 --> 01:05:41,485
Cthulhu is the ice cream of gaming.

1246
01:05:44,238 --> 01:05:46,139
I will tell you, it's always a little bit different.

1247
01:05:46,759 --> 01:05:47,940
Every designer's gonna tell you different.

1248
01:05:47,960 --> 01:05:49,300
Every time I work on a project's different.

1249
01:05:49,420 --> 01:05:52,082
I tend to do mechanics or mechanisms later,

1250
01:05:52,142 --> 01:05:52,882
but not always.

1251
01:05:53,842 --> 01:05:55,203
Sometimes it's theme or story.

1252
01:05:55,243 --> 01:05:57,424
Sometimes it's an emotional experience that I wanna get.

1253
01:05:57,484 --> 01:05:59,345
Sometimes I'm inspired by something way out.

1254
01:05:59,385 --> 01:06:01,086
I tend to be inspired outside of gaming

1255
01:06:01,106 --> 01:06:03,427
and then use gaming tools to make it a game.

1256
01:06:05,008 --> 01:06:07,230
So I might be inspired by television or,

1257
01:06:07,890 --> 01:06:09,151
like my daughter goes off to college,

1258
01:06:09,191 --> 01:06:10,352
my first child this fall, and so like,

1259
01:06:10,432 --> 01:06:11,793
what's that feel like?

1260
01:06:11,973 --> 01:06:13,334
And is there a game in that feeling?

1261
