The answer is probably no.

1262
01:06:15,716 --> 01:06:17,157
But like, that's like an interesting,

1263
01:06:17,177 --> 01:06:18,899
like how do I get people to an emotional space

1264
01:06:18,979 --> 01:06:19,899
or something like that?

1265
01:06:19,919 --> 01:06:22,161
So the inspiration comes from all different places,

1266
01:06:22,241 --> 01:06:25,424
but Susan McKinley Ross, I don't know if she's here,

1267
01:06:25,464 --> 01:06:26,765
but she did Quirkle and she talks about

1268
01:06:26,825 --> 01:06:28,486
how she does mechanics.

1269
