1278
01:06:43,416 --> 01:06:45,237
This is the very first class that we do

1279
01:06:45,457 --> 01:06:46,718
is experience first.

1280
01:06:46,778 --> 01:06:48,859
It's not mechanics, it's not theme, it's experience.

1281
01:06:48,879 --> 01:06:50,139
