1282
01:06:50,159 --> 01:06:51,320
I'm gonna do a zombie game,

1283
01:06:51,380 --> 01:06:53,521
which is the Cthulhu of two years ago, I guess.

1284
01:06:54,562 --> 01:06:57,124
