01:06:59,185 --> 01:07:03,709
You know, you've got to get to that experience, what I call the experience or the emotional core.

1287
01:07:04,089 --> 01:07:08,613
And I think that's what really carries you through, even if you end up totally changing the theme later,

1288
01:07:09,093 --> 01:07:11,976
if you've got that experience, or another way to look at it,

1289
01:07:12,056 --> 01:07:14,998
is the story that you want the players to tell when they're done.

1290
01:07:17,439 --> 01:07:21,911
Interesting. Player perspective, the end goal maybe rather than the start goal.

1291
01:07:22,412 --> 01:07:23,134
Thinking backwards.

