1337
01:09:10,877 --> 01:09:13,939
So, I mean, of course, the designer is the person that gets their name on the box,

1338
01:09:14,019 --> 01:09:18,162
because we're fragile creatures with egos that need constant attention.

1339
01:09:19,383 --> 01:09:24,808
I mean, of course, there's behind every board game. There's a development team, an art director, artists, a producer

1340
01:09:25,649 --> 01:09:31,874
and on the flip side, there's a sales team, marketing team, etc, etc, but

